# 🚀 Day 73/90 – Connect Flutter to Your FastAPI Backend

Welcome to **Day 73!**

Today is one of the biggest milestones in your project.

Until yesterday:

```text
Flutter App
     ↓
Sample Data
```

After today:

```text
Flutter App
      │
HTTP Request
      │
      ▼
FastAPI Backend
      │
JSON Response
      │
      ▼
Flutter App
```

This is your **first real client-server communication**.

---

# 🎯 Today's Goal

Your Flutter app will ask the backend:

```text
Are you running?
```

The backend will reply:

```json
{
   "status":"Healthy"
}
```

Flutter will display that response on the screen.

---

# Step 1

Open your Flutter project.

Open

```text
pubspec.yaml
```

---

